name: U N I Q U E S

metadata.name: Diothyma in Heaven's Smoke
metadata.description:
I've had very little time.
Even the evening's breath is cold.
I'm here like silent shadows, songs humming at my silent bedside, my slumbering heart trembles in my chest, and the shadows of melodious utterance live forever in dark clouds...
